Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just me, or are things getting worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that anomaly is gradually descending upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're receiving similar reports from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues, Earth will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the status of the three pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Still unable to confirm their location on any of our sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,how those guys felt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,when they chose to abandon Earth 20,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have just as much faith in Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This may sound funny coming from a relative of hers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's never let us down, not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When I want something to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She always finds a way to come through, no matter how serious she needs to become to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll fly to heights I can't even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing we can do is to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to trust Madoka and the others, and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the Vox,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we're so... powerless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss... What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I came by to bring Madoka her lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, we managed to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you guys can lend me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think happened to your brother, Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does this mean he was able to get back to the outside world?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The person next to him, is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This space we call the Rinne is connected
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to the hearts of those with a Memoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your will has changed this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of you have changed that man's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This place will close up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Yurikano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying here with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this because I love him or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Many lives were lost because of us, and I must atone for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want to make up for your mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have to start by being honest with your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take Lan's brother with us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after we leave here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the Jersey Club will be there to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad for something put together on the fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let me hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the continuation of where you left off 20,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cap! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The aurorae are combining into one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}When I hear a voice that moves my heart,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'll put on jersey and give it my all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Duty and obligation alone aren't enough to convince me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I leave it up to my heart to decide,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A song?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A song?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}on whether or not to take on a request.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Jersey Club Song!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Move forward! Move Forward!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Run! Run!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}That's the Jersey Club spirit!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cap! It's Aura, Lympha and Ignis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have their signals!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Vital signs normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All three pilots are alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we make it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Snap out of it, Lan!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look below. We made it home, to Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For a second, I thought this was the ocean on De Metrio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lan! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my brother! He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I could have your Kamogawa soup on board Pharos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! But I'm not full yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you plan on eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Asteria said there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also made younger, by about ten years, after returning from the Rinne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but he probably made the same wish as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To have a second chance in life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and pick up from where he left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rinne was a very magical place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish for something strong enough with all your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the Rinne can even reverse time itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happened to Lan's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had gone there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,would the same thing have happened to you, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I didn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I would be turned back,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,back to the me when I was always with you, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I love the way I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you have to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you leave us like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurikano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever leave without telling us again, you hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go, it'll be with the four of us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... and... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting damage reports
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,from branch offices around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like our work is just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like we've forgotten something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get that song out of my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that's the voice of the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That casual march can't be the voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Majestic, yet plaintive, but profound!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise it's meaningless to name that universe the "Rinne"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I made up that legend for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rinne isn't gone. And the Vox are still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll simply have to start anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, bon... appétit...  {timer - be careful with the "Ã©"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two on vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got off my early shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on break since
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,our Space University is closed for Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Golden Week in space?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, since we don't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,get much chance to see each other anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we would drop by to give Madoka photos
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,from our graduation trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you leaving today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you waiting for Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I came by because she wanted to ask me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the ocean on Le Garite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I called earlier, she said she'd be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Madoka's gotten even busier since she graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just like Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Madoka's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wondered why she was always so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never quite figure her out, despite being her kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel like I'm wasting my time waiting for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will you be going this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Chairman is full of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She mentioned something about the Bermuda Triangle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,holding the key that connects the Rinne to the depths of the Earth's oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm guessing that's where we'll start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope today and tomorrow will be a happy day for me, and for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you supposed to be leaving today, Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I came all the way here because you said you wanted to ask me something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow- oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that time ten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when I nearly drowned?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:16:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered why I went into the water that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ever tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I jumped into the ocean because I wanted to see Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, she wasn't there, and the next thing I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to die, but that's when Midori poked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that was Mom telling me to snap out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe what you want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Le Garite...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still a week away on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to dress like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly can't attend dressed like a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so you're really going to become a cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's a good time to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even know how to cook things besides pasta, Izo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That fried egg thing you made was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So simple, yet profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are making fun of me, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was starting to think that you wouldn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a hard time finding jersey that would fit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How's everything going for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, life can't get any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the flower
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that bloomed on the ship that left Earth 20,000 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and has since been cared for by the Le Garite royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To De Metrio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not kings anymore, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All the more reason you'll be able
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep a single flower in bloom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we really are starting over from scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I wasn't trying to skip out or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my new boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the Kamo-Girls' Jersey Club, KISS Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Branch Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really have to call you by that title?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! After all, Madoka is the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have to call ourselves the Jersey Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have reports of yet another miracle resulting{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from the abnormal meteorological phenomena which took place late last year.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With regard to the Polyhedron 1000-year problem and measures to deal with the impending collision{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of Le Garite and De Metrio,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a detailed study conducted by a committee{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}noted a large change in the orbits of both planets...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Novumundus Chairman Asteria Lizamarie De Roschefall,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}now also the committee's chairman, promised to make public all data.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't. We're helping with setting up the shopping district for the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}And released a statement saying: "It means everything's a success now!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the Secretary-General of which United Nations?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, but I have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Send me an e-mail with the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise we'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't go anywhere in the Polyhedron without this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We were getting tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I made lunches for you two as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't do without this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:21:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be helping out at the Space Fireworks Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and then be at the De Metrio Nursing Home recreation meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget our visit to the children's home in the Pa-Dros Star System.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have to attend a clean-up demonstration at the Intergalactic Debris Meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be coming home at...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, so I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, be careful, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone loved the song you girls sang
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at the unveiling of the Tanpopo Children's Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Success!
